data.description: Discover Your Dream Home. Step into this enchanting 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom haven and instantly feel the warmth of family moments waiting to be made. Imagine the holidays and your own space to spread out and entertain. The vaulted ceilings with rustic wood beams in the living room create an inviting atmosphere, while the kitchen, a culinary delight, offers abundant cabinet space and elegant wooden cabinets. Embrace the outdoor paradise, perfect for savoring Texas BBQ on your covered rustic porch, where memories with loved ones come alive. The sound of music and laughter are just waiting for their opportunity here. Don't miss out on making this dream a reality. Schedule a viewing today and let this property become your new home sweet home! Roof replaced in 2019. Current Survey available.
